    &lt;p&gt;Hereâ€™s a quick walkthrough for using  &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/carrierwaveuploader/carrierwave&quot;&gt;Carrierwave&lt;/a&gt; with
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/jubos/fake-s3&quot;&gt;FakeS3&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are going to use &lt;code&gt;fakes3.local&lt;/code&gt; for the hostname, &lt;code&gt;3100&lt;/code&gt; for the port and &lt;code&gt;my-bucket&lt;/code&gt; for the s3 bucket name.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Install the &lt;code&gt;fakes3&lt;/code&gt; gem:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot; data-lang=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;gem install fakes3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Associate &lt;code&gt;fakes3.local&lt;/code&gt; with your local computer:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot; data-lang=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# /etc/hosts&lt;/span&gt;
127.0.0.1 fakes3.local&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Edit the carrierwave initializer:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# config/initializers/carrierwave.rb&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CarrierWave&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;configure&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;fog_provider&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;fog/aws&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;fog_credentials&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;provider&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;AWS&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;aws_access_key_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;aws_secret_access_key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;                  &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;fakes3.local&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;scheme&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;                &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;http&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;path_style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;            &lt;span class=&quot;kp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;port&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;                  &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;3100&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;fog_directory&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;my-bucket&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Finally, run fakes3:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot; data-lang=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;fakes3 --root&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;tmp/fakes3_root --port&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;3100&lt;/span&gt; --hostname&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;fakes3.local&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//nickgal.github.io/blog/using-carrierwave-with-fakes3/&quot;&gt;Using Carrierwave With FakeS3&lt;/a&gt; was originally published by Nick Gal at &lt;a href=&quot;//nickgal.github.io/blog&quot;&gt;Nick Gal&lt;/a&gt; on November 16, 2015.&lt;/p&gt;
